    Megatron shighs as he looks out onto the battle feild. That little dog 
was supposed to have settled this thing. He went out, and opened fire.

    Waspinator soars down from the sky and dives right into the bunker 
opening like a flash. He jets down the tunnle, and sets down in the Triangle 
room.
    "Hello mouse bot!" He said to Darkmouse, and then walked past them to 
Black Aracnia.
    "Megatron wants to know why you cut of communications. Hes very mad...."
    Aracnia shook her head. "Tell him to come here, now that the communicator 
is broken. Take Atma and his ally with you to assist in the battle. Ok?"
    Waspinator nodded and turned to Darkmouse. "Bub bye mousey. Hehehe." And 
then flew away.
